  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.8.10">
<l>vaṇṭār poḻilcūḻn taḻakā yanāṅkūr maṇimā ṭa<supplied>k</supplied>kōyil neṭumā lukkeṉṟum</l>
<l>toṇṭā yatolcīr vayalmaṅ kaiyarkkōṉ kaliya ṉolicey tamiḻmā laivallār,</l>
<l>kaṇṭār vaṇaṅkak kaḷiyā ṉaimītē kaṭalcū ḻulakuk kōrukā valarāy</l>
<l>viṇṭōy neṭuveṇ kuṭainī ḻaliṉkīḻ virinī rulakāṇ ṭuvirum puvarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who masters this Tamil garland composed of the words of Kaliyaṉ,</l>
<l rend="indent">king of those of ancient Maṅkai with fine paddy fields,</l>
<l>Having become eternally in service to tall Māl in the Maṇimāṭa Temple</l>
<l rend="indent">of beautiful Nānkūr encircled by bee-filled gardens,</l>
<l>As a guardian of the sea-girded earth, [riding] upon a rutting elephant,</l>
<l rend="indent">as those who see [him] bow,</l>
<l>He will rejoice, ruling the wide, watered world</l>
<l rend="indent">[from] under the shade of a tall, white umbrella which touches the sky.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
